Patch B: save MP4 instead of interactive display
Matplotlib‚Äôs FuncAnimation makes an animation by repeatedly calling an update function (func) over a frames sequence.
5

Matplotlib‚Äôs Animation.save is explicitly documented as saving the animation ‚Äúby drawing every frame.‚Äù
7

To run in a non-GUI context, Matplotlib also documents that selecting the "Agg" backend is sufficient for rendering without a graphical front-end.
8

Minimal MP4 save change:

